ActIndian Band Election Regulations
SubjectPinaymootang First Nation - Indian Band Election Regulations
PrecisOrder acknowledging receipt of the report of the Minister of Indigenous Services, indicating that there was a violation of the INDIAN BAND ELECTION REGULATIONS that may have affected the results of the October 28, 2017 election of the council of the PINAYMOOTANG FIRST NATION, located in Manitoba.
